                        <h2 class="fundName"><a href="/ucp/books/funds/bevingtonFund.html" class="noline">The Bevington Fund</a></h2>
                        
                        <p class="description"><p>The Bevington Fund&nbsp; helps publish work by emerging scholars and is used in support of first books, particularly in the humanities. The fund was established in 2006 with a $100,000 gift by David and Peggy Bevington, which has been augmented by students, friends, and a foundation.</p></p>


