                    <div class="slab-bordered">
                        <h2 class="fundName"><a href="/ucp/books/funds/meijerFoundationFund.html" class="noline">The Meijer Foundation Fund</a></h2>
                        
                        <p class="description"><p>Endowed in 2018 by a generous gift from the Meijer Foundation of Grand Rapids, Michigan, this fund supports the publication of books of enduring interest in the disciplines of American political history, political science, and related areas. In recognition of the Meijer family&rsquo;s connection to the greater Midwest, special consideration is given to books and authors that are grounded in the history and culture of the Great Lakes region.</p></p>


